00:39:52.690 --> 00:39:54.559 align:middle line:84%
A little hyper anyway so it
helps.

00:39:54.559 --> 00:39:57.095 align:middle line:84%
When I see you in action, you
do,

00:39:57.095 --> 00:39:59.664 align:middle line:84%
you get very very fast and
spirit comes in

00:39:59.664 --> 00:40:01.499 align:middle line:90%
and you tell them to slow down.

00:40:01.499 --> 00:40:03.301 align:middle line:84%
Slow down yes, because they are
too fast.

00:40:03.301 --> 00:40:04.902 align:middle line:90%
It moves very very quickly.

00:40:04.902 --> 00:40:08.206 align:middle line:84%
They'll be like sending me
thoughts and images.

00:40:08.206 --> 00:40:09.741 align:middle line:90%
It's very much like if I say,

00:40:09.741 --> 00:40:11.676 align:middle line:90%
"Hello, how are you today?"

00:40:11.676 --> 00:40:13.244 align:middle line:90%
The spirit way would say,

00:40:13.244 --> 00:40:14.679 align:middle line:90%
"Hello-you-today."

00:40:14.679 --> 00:40:17.982 align:middle line:84%
It's so quick and many times
they'll get through,

00:40:17.982 --> 00:40:18.883 align:middle line:90%
let's say a name.

00:40:18.883 --> 00:40:21.252 align:middle line:90%
It will say "Mary. Mary."

00:40:21.252 --> 00:40:22.420 align:middle line:90%
And I will hear "Mary."

00:40:22.420 --> 00:40:23.921 align:middle line:84%
So, I'll say "There's a lady
here named Mary."

00:40:23.921 --> 00:40:24.889 align:middle line:84%
The person in the audience will
say

00:40:24.889 --> 00:40:28.526 align:middle line:90%
her name is Marie, not Mary.

00:40:28.526 --> 00:40:30.194 align:middle line:90%
But you see how close it is.

00:40:30.194 --> 00:40:30.862 align:middle line:90%
That's what you hear.

