00:40:36.534 --> 00:40:38.269 align:middle line:90%
Flooding images?

00:40:38.269 --> 00:40:39.537 align:middle line:90%
All different.

00:40:39.537 --> 00:40:42.707 align:middle line:84%
I'll see them as pictures, as
blending of pictures.

00:40:42.707 --> 00:40:44.976 align:middle line:84%
I'll see a person standing
there and they'll look

00:40:44.976 --> 00:40:47.078 align:middle line:84%
physically I'm looking at you
right now?

00:40:47.078 --> 00:40:48.179 align:middle line:90%
It's exactly that.

00:40:48.179 --> 00:40:50.848 align:middle line:84%
Or I'll see just a head or I'll
see just a face

00:40:50.848 --> 00:40:52.917 align:middle line:90%
or I'll see a beautiful suit.

00:40:52.917 --> 00:40:54.852 align:middle line:84%
Something how they can project
into my consciousness

00:40:54.852 --> 00:40:57.755 align:middle line:84%
an image, a thought, that I'm
able to give to the person

00:40:57.755 --> 00:40:59.257 align:middle line:90%
that they understand it's them.

00:40:59.257 --> 00:41:01.592 align:middle line:84%
I'm known as a Survival
Evidence Medium,

00:41:01.592 --> 00:41:03.127 align:middle line:84%
which means that my job is
really to

00:41:03.127 --> 00:41:05.563 align:middle line:84%
