00:41:07.265 --> 00:41:08.766 align:middle line:90%
that only that person would know

00:41:08.766 --> 00:41:09.901 align:middle line:90%
and the spirit would know.

00:41:09.901 --> 00:41:11.469 align:middle line:84%
It proves survivor
consciousness.

00:41:11.469 --> 00:41:12.537 align:middle line:90%
