00:41:14.639 --> 00:41:15.340 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:41:15.340 --> 00:41:15.940 align:middle line:90%
Or the government?

00:41:15.940 --> 00:41:17.642 align:middle line:10%
Yes, I used to do a lot of work
with

00:41:17.642 --> 00:41:19.677 align:middle line:10%
police agencies.

00:41:19.677 --> 00:41:21.846 align:middle line:10%
Years and years ago, I used to
work mostly

00:41:21.846 --> 00:41:24.048 align:middle line:10%
in kidnapping cases.

00:41:24.048 --> 00:41:27.185 align:middle line:10%
Quietly, off to the side, I've
worked

00:41:27.185 --> 00:41:28.820 align:middle line:90%
on some well-known cases too,

00:41:28.820 --> 00:41:30.054 align:middle line:84%
which I'm not going to talk
about.

00:41:30.054 --> 00:41:32.724 align:middle line:90%
But I have worked in some cases.

00:41:32.724 --> 00:41:34.325 align:middle line:90%
Interesting stuff.

00:41:34.325 --> 00:41:36.794 align:middle line:84%
I saw files of some of these
things.

00:41:36.794 --> 00:41:39.197 align:middle line:84%
But, when the kidnapping thing
happened,

00:41:39.197 --> 00:41:41.699 align:middle line:84%
and there's a movie, my movie
with Ted Danson,

00:41:41.699 --> 00:41:43.835 align:middle line:84%
